  "stem": "<p><math><mn>4</mn><mi>u</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>9</mn><mi>v</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>w</mi></math></p><p>The given equation relates the variables <em>u</em>, <em>v</em>, and <em>w</em>. Which equation correctly expresses <em>v</em> in terms of <em>u</em> and <em>w</em>?</p>",
